Package: visPedigree
Type: Package
Title: Tidying, Analysis, and Fast Visualization of Animal and Plant Pedigrees
Version: 1.6.2
Authors@R: person("Sheng","Luan", email="luansheng@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for the standardization, statistical analysis, 
    and fast visualization of animal and plant pedigrees. It robustly handles 
    complex mating systems, such as selfing and monoecious reproduction. Core 
    analytical methods compute generation intervals, effective population size, 
    founder and ancestor contributions, partial inbreeding, genetic relationship 
    matrices, and inbreeding coefficients using optimized C++ algorithms and the 
    'data.table' framework. For exploration, it uses 'igraph' to offer scalable 
    network graphing and matrix plotting methods, simplifying the visualization 
    of deep genealogies and large full-sib families.
License: GPL-3
